text:
<@U0W7D64LC>:  thank you for your suggestions. 
1. I added the link to the use case index  to the project's home page. 
2. Good idea with  the mailing lists . Will create these lists once we have any use cases ready.
3. Could you explain 'we’re neglecting the proposals' please? Do I understand you correctly we need to first develop the use cases suitable to the projects in the incubator, i.e. develop the ones where the need for a permissioned chain is clear, i.e. Settlement Use Case vs Charity?

new wiki page to track development of the use cases
<https://github.com/hyperledger/hyperledger/wiki/Use-Case-Development-Dashboard>
